column2: Are you really going across the plains to California? Are you not afraid of being burned black by the sun and wind?
How did you send your house to California? We sent it on a flatfornia
So you wanna know how to get to California A? So first you gotta get up too …… and then you will be at Cal-I-FORN-IA
I heard that they kept the flower- scoops to scoop the gold out of the barrels
